Harmony Gold to Restart Operations at Masimong Shaft After Death of Worker

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-04-20T06:48:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-20/harmony-gold-to-restart-operations-at-masimong-shaft-after-death-of-worker.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. will
restart operations at the No. 5 shaft of its Masimong mine in
 South Africa  today after the government lifted a safety
suspension, spokeswoman Marian van der Walt said by mobile
phone.  The shaft was temporarily closed after the death of a
worker in an accident on April 14.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mkhululi Mancotywa in Johannesburg at 
 mmancotywa1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
